text: Zhou Ping or Zhouping may refer to: *King Ping of Zhou or Zhou Ping Wang (died 720 BC), king of the Zhou dynasty *Zhou Ping (gymnast) (born 1968), Chinese gymnast *Zhouping, Zhuzhou, a township in Hunan Province, China *Zhouping Xin ( 1988–2004), Chinese mathematician ==See also== *Ping Zhou (researcher), researcher with ANSYS *Zhou Pingjian ( 2016), Chinese ambassador to Nigeria
title: Zhou Ping
